      <title>BYD销售飙升以上，超过1000亿美元，超过了特斯拉的收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-24/byd-sales-soar-past-100-billion-tops-tesla-on-revenue-video</link>
